nodes.title: Inpainting
widgets_values:
1) Upload your image 

2) Right click on the node and Click "open in mask Editor" 

3) Draw your mask and click save to node

4) Optional - Upscale Image if you feel the Masked area is very small to get proper details.

nodes.title: Outpainting
widgets_values:
1) Unmute the Nodes and Upload your image.

2) Set Outpainting - Padding Value

3) Connect the reroute nodes to activate the outpainting pipline

4) Use Mask Expand and Blur setting if you see visible seams.

nodes.title: Inpainting or Outpainting ?
widgets_values: Connect Inpainting Or Outpainting Group Reroute Nodes
